OL,3,CMore than 8,000 social media accounts
OL,4,Clinked to people smuggling taken down
OL,6,FMore than 8,000 social media accounts
OL,7,Flinked to people smuggling were taken
OL,8,Fdown following referrals from the
OL,9,FNational Crime Agency (NCA) last year,
OL,10,Fthe law enforcement body said.
OL,12,FThis was a 40% increase from the 5,600
OL,13,Faccounts removed in 2023, and means
OL,14,Fmore than 16,500 have been taken down
OL,15,Fin total since the NCA launched its
OL,16,Fsocial media action plan with Meta, X
OL,17,F(formerly known as Twitter), TikTok
OL,18,Fand YouTube in December 2021.
