OL,3,CMore than 8,000 social media accounts
OL,4,Clinked to people smuggling taken down
OL,6,FThe accounts taken down in the course
OL,7,Fof the operation included posts that
OL,8,Ffalsely promoted small boat crossings
OL,9,Ffrom France to the UK as being via
OL,10,Fspeedboat and offered prizes to
OL,11,Fmigrants who referred a friend, as
OL,12,Fwell as fake ID documents for sale.
OL,14,FOthers also offered transport from
OL,15,FAfrica to southern Europe.
