OL,6,F"Taking down these accounts disrupts
OL,7,Fthe activities of those criminal
OL,8,Fnetworks, we are devoting more
OL,9,Fresources to doing that as it is one
OL,10,Fof a number of ways we can actively
OL,11,Ftarget them and make their life more
OL,12,Fdifficult."
OL,14,FAmanj Hasan Zada, from Preston, was
OL,15,Fconvicted and jailed for 17 years in
OL,16,FNovember after it was found he used
OL,17,Fvideo testimonials of those he had
OL,18,Fsuccessfully smuggled to promote
OL,19,Fhimself.
